16/03/2011
TIRANA, Albania -- Albania marked on Tuesday (March 15th) the 3rd anniversary of the Gerdec tragedy in which an ammunitions depot exploded, killing 26 people and injuring 300. 
Survivors visited the site of the explosion, which damaged hundreds of houses. 
Legal proceedings drag on, involving 30 people accused in the case. 
(Balkan Web, Alsat, Klan, Top News - 15/03/11)
